extends layout

block content
  div.text-center
    img(style="max-width:100%;", src="/images/logo.png")
    h1.text-center BorisBike.me - the bike balancer project
    p.lead.text-center Improve your community by helping balancing bikes around London!
  hr
  if !user
    .row
      .col-md-4
        h2 How it works?
        p When you're near an overflowed docking station, we'll send you a notification. If you open it, we tell you where to move a bike. You cycle and win points. That simple!
        p.text-center
          a.btn.btn-default(href='/signup', role='button') Sign up
      .col-md-4
        h2 Hate the guesswork?
        p Text 'hint' to 04327532524 and we'll let you know where to start. Sign up now and get 3 free hints!
      .col-md-4
        h2 Make London Better
        p Balancing bikes will eventually remove the vans that are currently use to do this task. And you get to exercise a bit. And there's more: we have awesome prizes coming up soon!

  else
    .row
      .col-md-4
        h2 Go out! We notify you when you can help!
        p We'll send a notification straight to your phone when you're near a docking station that has an overflow of bikes.

      .col-md-4
        h2 Don't want to wait? Get a hint!
        p A hint costs a credit. You currently have #{user.credits} credits.
        p.text-center
          a.btn.btn-default(href='/get-credits', role='button') Buy more credits

      .col-md-4
        h2 Text 'hint' at 074325426435.
        p We'll text you back a location so you can start cycling without the guesswork!
